# Title: Application Terminated Via Wmic.EXE
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2023-09-11
# Level: medium
# Description: Detects calls to the "terminate" function via wmic in order to kill an application
# MITRE Tactic: Execution
# Tags: attack.execution, attack.t1047
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_wmic_terminate_application.yml

CommandLine="*call*" CommandLine="*terminate*" Image="*\\WMIC.exe" OR OriginalFileName="wmic.exe"